    <item>
      <title>随着加沙死亡人数增加，以色列和美国之间的紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/israel-hamas-war-revealing-tension-between-biden-netanyahu-over-gaza-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几乎每天都打的电话几个月前就停止了。现在，乔·拜登和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡之间因以色列对哈马斯战争而产生的紧张关系随着两位领导人公开争吵而公开化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/israel-hamas-war-revealing-tension-between-biden-netanyahu-over-gaza-deaths</guid>
